  "text": "Serum irisin concentration was measured using the enzymelinked immunosorbent assay (ELISA) kits (Aviscera Biosciences, Santa Clara, CA). The assay was proven to be highly sensitive to human irisin [CITATION_1] . The sensitivity of the assay was 0.2 ng/ml and the linear range of the standard was 5 to 500 ng/ml. The intraand inter-assay variations were both less than 10%.",
